title: Stock market news live updates: Stocks fall as S&P 500, Dow attempt to notch second week of gains - Yahoo Finance
content: Stock market news live updates: Stocks fall as S&P 500, Dow attempt to notch second week of gains  Yahoo Finance
description: U.S. stocks rose Friday to build on gains from an up day on Wall Street that saw all three major indexes close sharply higher in the previous trading session as investors further mulled the path forward for interest rates and a host of new sanctions against Russia.
